data.description: Welcome home to this 4BR/2.5 bath 2 story home with 2 car attached garage. In the heart of Boiling Springs close to schools, general shopping and easy access to I-85. Over 2300 square feet of living space!! Great kitchen with ample cabinet space, washer/dryer to convey with the property!! Large master bedroom with full bath attached, jetted tub and walk in closets. 3 great sized bedrooms with a full bath and additional half bath. Large living area with stone and shiplap gas log fireplace for these cold winter nights!! Over a half acre lot with inground pool. Pool has a new liner and new filter! Roof was replaced right before 27 solar panels installed for energy efficiency. Seller will pay off solar panels at closing with acceptable offer. Gutter guards were installed so no more cleaning out gutters!! This is a great home in a terrific location, call for your appointment today!
